score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:41:02.000Z","msg":"靠自己買，係你名，又供斷，確實可以睇唔起公屋仔，呢個係你個人自由。靠屋企既，叻極咪係識投胎。"},{"pid":"7754fd99d00676a1c0f06bd2bffc78256758dbfb","tid":125300,"uid":82543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T19:28:49.000Z","msg":"上面好多公屋仔打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d012bbfbb7ccbb75f147f12cbbd3a0f5f5ee47","tid":125300,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T19:41:09.000Z","msg":"今時今日竟然仲有人認為公屋=窮撚，大把人收埋 D 車樓，寧願租俾人收租自己就住返公屋"},{"pid":"f6e5261e3000b44d7d38337abd4ff81616765b64","tid":125300,"uid":82543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今時今日竟然仲有人認為公屋=窮撚，大把人收埋 D 車樓，寧願租俾人收租自己就住返公屋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公屋仔"},{"pid":"dca42b121d2418b5e57f00930dce0e9ea76622a5","tid":125300,"uid":82543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:42:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今時今日竟然仲有人認為公屋=窮撚，大把人收埋 D 車樓，寧願租俾人收租自己就住返公屋</blockquote><br />\n唔係窮撚既 至少買唔起新樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你死都要話大陸有咩咩咩係手 又吹你唔脹<br />\n自己知就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}